        lesson("rel-05", "Boundaries", "A boundary describes your action", "A boundary states what you will do to protect safety, time, or dignity. It is different from a threat meant to control another person.", "Use: If shouting begins, I will pause and leave the conversation.", "Love is Respect · Boundaries", "https://www.loveisrespect.org/resources/what-are-my-boundaries/"),
