        lesson("rel-08", "Connection", "Social connection supports health", "Supportive relationships can protect health and well-being. Connection quality matters; being around people is not automatically the same as feeling safe or supported.", "Choose one person with whom a small honest contact is possible.", "CDC · Social connectedness", "https://www.cdc.gov/social-connectedness/about/index.html"),
