        lesson("hea-02", "Movement", "Strength belongs in the week", "Adult activity guidance includes muscle-strengthening activity in addition to aerobic movement. Exercises and loads should fit current capacity.", "Choose one comfortable push, pull, squat, or carry pattern to learn.", "HHS · Physical Activity Guidelines", "https://health.gov/our-work/nutrition-physical-activity/physical-activity-guidelines"),
