        lesson("hea-04", "Nutrition", "Fiber is a family of compounds", "Different fibers affect digestion differently. Beans, whole grains, vegetables, fruit, nuts, and seeds add variety; rapid increases can cause discomfort.", "Add one tolerated fiber-rich food and increase gradually.", "NIDDK · Eating and digestion", "https://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/digestive-diseases"),
